name: iShares U.S. Equity High Income UCITS ETF USD (Acc)
description_en: The iShares U.S. Equity High Income UCITS ETF USD (Acc) is an actively managed ETF. The ETF invests in companies from the US. Title selection is based on quantitative (mathematical or statistical) forecast models and ESG criteria. Furthermore, the ETF aims to generate additional income by selling call options and buying futures on a US large cap equity index. The ETF's TER (total expense ratio) amounts to 0.35% p.a.. The dividends in the ETF are accumulated and reinvested in the ETF. The iShares U.S. Equity High Income UCITS ETF USD (Acc) is a very small ETF with 1m Euro assets under management. The ETF was launched on 22 March 2024 and is domiciled in Ireland.

Výběr titulu je založen na kvantitativních (matematických nebo statistických) prognózech modelů a kritérií ESG. Cílem ETF je dále vygenerovat další příjem prodejem možností hovoru a nákupem futures na americký index s velkým kapitálem. TER (celkový poměr nákladů) činí 0,35% p.a. dividenday v ETF jsou akumulovány a reinvestovány do ETF. IShares USA Equity High Income UCITS ETF USD (ACC) je velmi malý ETF s 1m euro ve spravování. ETF byl spuštěn 22. března 2024 a má bydliště v Irsku.

name: WisdomTree Industrial Metals Longer Dated
description_en: The WisdomTree Industrial Metals Longer Dated seeks to track the Bloomberg Industrial Metals 3 Month Forward index. The Bloomberg Industrial Metals 3 Month Forward index tracks commodities from the industrial metals segment. The index is a forward index that represents the Bloomberg Industrial Metals index three months in future. The ETC's TER (total expense ratio) amounts to 0.49% p.a.. The WisdomTree Industrial Metals Longer Dated is the only ETC that tracks the Bloomberg Industrial Metals 3 Month Forward index. The ETC replicates the performance of the underlying index synthetically with a swap. The WisdomTree Industrial Metals Longer Dated is a very small ETC with 1m Euro assets under management. The ETC was launched on 10 October 2007 and is domiciled in Jersey.

TER (celkový poměr nákladů) ETC činí 0,49% p.a. Průmyslové kovy WisdomTree Delded je jediné atd., Které sleduje průmyslové kovy Bloomberg 3 měsíce vpřed. name: JPMorgan Japan Research Enhanced Index Equity (ESG) UCITS ETF CHF Hedged (acc)
description_en: The JPMorgan Japan Research Enhanced Index Equity (ESG) UCITS ETF CHF Hedged (acc) is an actively managed ETF. The JP Morgan Japan Research Enhanced Index Equity (ESG) (CHF Hedged) Strategy invests in companies from Japan. This fund seeks to generate a higher return than the MSCI Japan index. In addition, the fund management avoids companies whose ESG performance has a negative impact on operations or whose business practices do not conform to the fund management's standards. Currency hedged to Swiss Francs (CHF). The ETF's TER (total expense ratio) amounts to 0.25% p.a.. The dividends in the ETF are accumulated and reinvested in the ETF. The JPMorgan Japan Research Enhanced Index Equity (ESG) UCITS ETF CHF Hedged (acc) is a very small ETF with 1m Euro assets under management. The ETF was launched on 9 August 2022 and is domiciled in Ireland.

name: AXA IM MSCI World Equity PAB UCITS ETF USD Dist
description_en: The AXA IM MSCI World Equity PAB UCITS ETF USD Dist seeks to track the MSCI World Climate Paris Aligned index. The MSCI World Climate Paris Aligned index tracks stocks from developed countries worldwide. The index aims to give greater weight to companies that benefit from the transition to a lower carbon economy. In addition, EU directives on climate protection are taken into account. The parent index is the MSCI World. The ETF's TER (total expense ratio) amounts to 0.20% p.a.. The ETF replicates the performance of the underlying index by full replication (buying all the index constituents). The dividends in the ETF are distributed to the investors (Semi annually). The AXA IM MSCI World Equity PAB UCITS ETF USD Dist is a very small ETF with 1m Euro assets under management. The ETF was launched on 16 July 2024 and is domiciled in Ireland.
description_cs: Světový kapitál AXA IM MSCI PAB UCITS ETF USD Dist se snaží sledovat index MSCI World Climate Paříž. Světový indexový index MSCI World Climate Paříž sleduje akcie z rozvinutých zemí po celém světě. Cílem indexu je poskytnout větší váhu společnostem, které těží z přechodu na nižší uhlíkovou ekonomiku. Kromě toho se berou v úvahu směrnice EU o ochraně klimatu. Rodičovský index je svět MSCI. TER (celkový poměr výdajů) ETF činí 0,20% p.a. ETF replikuje výkon podkladového indexu plnou replikací (nákup všech indexových složek). dividenday v ETF jsou distribuovány investorům (polo každoročně). Světový kapitál AXA IM MSCI PAB UCITS ETF USD DIST je velmi malý ETF s řízením 1 milionu euro. ETF byl spuštěn 16. července 2024 a je se sídlem v Irsku.
